48:41.280 --> 48:42.691
You want to invest?
We got the gold.

48:42.800 --> 48:44.216
We can talk about it.

48:44.240 --> 48:45.969
Don't need a fucking partner.
I know that.

48:46.080 --> 48:48.447
You know,
there's something about...

48:48.560 --> 48:50.961
