missing here in the city.

49:17.160 --> 49:19.480
It's what makes it so hard for
us to have this conversation

49:19.520 --> 49:22.126
because you have never felt it.

49:23.600 --> 49:26.809
So I have a proposal for you.

49:26.920 --> 49:28.843
Put together
your institutional players,

49:28.960 --> 49:32.328
the guys who rep the big money.

49:32.440 --> 49:35.489
Whoever needs to kick
the tires on this thing.

49:35.600 --> 49:38.809
I will take them
on a little trip up the river.

49:40.640 --> 49:43.644
So... it was Acosta

49:43.760 --> 49:46.127
