together?

49:48.960 --> 49:51.486
Oh, Jennings, you're...
you're not getting it.

49:51.600 --> 49:55.446
Look, we-we didn't feel like
we had to cook up anything.

49:55.560 --> 49:57.847
I mean, I had people
coming at me from all sides.

49:57.960 --> 49:59.769
