in a radiating pattern

51:16.240 --> 51:19.244
and we kept going until
we had the definitive picture.

51:19.360 --> 51:21.886
We're mapping
the underlying geology.

51:22.000 --> 51:25.561
The cores are cut into
sections, and then crushed.

51:27.000 --> 51:29.685
